  <brief_title>Pilot Study of Abbreviated Chemotherapy Based on Positron Emission Tomography (PET) Scan in Hodgkin's Lymphoma</brief_title>
  <official_title>Pilot Study of Abbreviated Chemotherapy Based on Positron Emission Tomography in Hodgkin Lymphoma</official_title>
